titleInfo.title: Lia et al v. Nebraska Department of Correctional Services
titleInfo.subTitle: MEMORANDUM AND ORDER granting 2 Motion for Leave to Proceed in forma pauperis. Plaintiff shall pay an initial partial filing fee of $.03 by 9/15/08. The Clerk is directed to send a copy of this order to the appropriate official at plaintiff's institution. The Clerk is directed to set a pro se case management deadline for 9/15/08: initial partial filing fee payment due. Ordered by Judge Laurie Smith Camp. (Copies mailed to pro se party and Inga Hookstra, Accounting/Finance Manager, Nebraska Department of Correctional Services, Central Office Accounting, PO Box 94661, Lincoln, NE 68508) (JSF)
